reviewText: Since I saw my first Bond movie I became amazed, everytime I went to the video store i rented out one. I have loved Bond movies for years. Anyway this giftset has a collection of some amazing Bond films you have to see to belive. It contains some of my favourite bonds, i.e, Sean Connery. If you are Bond fan like me you must buy this giftset for either yourself or for someone else.
